abstract: "This repository contains the causRCA dataset and benchmark framework for automated root cause analysis and causal discovery in manufacturing. The dataset provides real-world industrial scenarios with ground truth causal graphs, enabling comprehensive evaluation of causal inference and RCA algorithms. The accompanying code facilitates benchmarking studies and comparative analysis of different approaches."
